{"tid":7732,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我地輕音樂同好會去左和紗屋企合宿","createTime":"2016-11-28T03:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T13:23:16.000Z","uid":6527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c68ff3b572aee359c72c768b500e0abe135e1cd4","tid":7732,"uid":6527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:20:46.000Z","msg":"其實我都係第一次去和紗屋企 真係好大好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我留意到有位成員好似好熟悉和紗屋企咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢連邊到開燈 地面邊到有電線都知得一清二楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩我去廁所沖涼個陣 仲發現多左個旅行套裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明我係第一個沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/28/111852_52d1971e90245c65aa3aa1bd203e177d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F28%2F111852_52d1971e90245c65aa3aa1bd203e177d.jpg&h=ec625670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我懷疑個位成員一早已經去過和紗屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位動物台手足 我應唔應該問清楚佢地 定係當睇唔到扮唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a6745ea426b0f443e3ae6ee6a7b8cbc45ddb72","tid":7732,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:24:02.000Z","msg":"俾我揀10次<br />\n10次都一定雪菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6e62c3770dc68cbb486830c2b4a724439884a7","tid":7732,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:24:41.000Z","msg":"btw 巴打你高登名係邊個啊"},{"pid":"30e677c9a6227606b6d8b6903b7f8807ef952e1e","tid":7732,"uid":6527